<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.eqknights.com/awards/shield_of_nobility.gif " style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END-->  Shield of Nobility<br>
<br>
6/20/02:<br>
The Shield of Nobility is hereby awarded to Dami Valorton and to Amazine for their help in the acquisition of a Key to Charisis for Loralis. Dami's generosity, both for including Loralis in the roll for the Fang of Xalgoz and for giving it to him when he himself won it, was unexpected and unasked for, and an act far above and beyond the code. Amazine then helped Loralis camp the Chancellor of Di'Zok, refusing to roll and insisting that Loralis take the Jade Chodikai Prod since he already had the fang. Again, an inspiring act of generosity.These actions prove these individuals as more than just Knights. Congratulations on your awards! (Sub=Charcoth) <br>
