<br>
Awarded on 6-28-00, at lvl 37, for saving the life of Aerren Evilslayer. <br>
<br>
While in Mistmoore Dami and Aerren were making an escape from the jail to the zone. At the Grave Yard entrance they encountered a hoard of Ushers and other higher Mobs returning from the zone. The onslaught stunned Aerren at the gorge and was zapping his life quickly. Aerren knew his LoH was expired with one bubble of health left he though he was a goner. Dami Valorton (being beat on himself) returned to Aerren and expended his LoH undoubtedly saving the life of Aerren Evilslayer and provided him enough time to make it to the zone. Both the Knights lived to fight again. Dami did not feel he put himself in serious danger. (Sub &amp; wit: Aerren Evilslayer.)<br>
